## Cluster Quality
- **Silhouette Score:** {sil_score:.3f} {"(Excellent)" if sil_score > 0.7 else "(Good)" if sil_score > 0.5 else "(Moderate)"}
- **Davies-Bouldin Score:** {db_score:.3f} {"(Good < 1.0)" if db_score < 1.0 else "(Needs improvement)"}

## Cluster Distribution
| Cluster | Count | Percentage |
|---------|-------|------------|
"""

for k, v in cluster_size_summary.items():
    mining_report += f"| {k} | {v['count']} | {v['pct']}% |\n"

mining_report += f"""
## Cluster Profiles
"""

for pattern in top_patterns:
    mining_report += f"""
### Cluster {pattern['cluster']} — {pattern['size']} employees ({pattern['percentage']}%)
